      <h3>Sources</h3>
      <table>
        <tr><td>Idaho Code 49-948</td><td><a href="https://legislature.idaho.gov/statutesrules/idstat/title49/t49ch9/sect49-948/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">legislature.idaho.gov</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Idaho 511</td><td><a href="https://511.idaho.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">511.idaho.gov</a></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Idaho Transportation Department</td><td><a href="https://itd.idaho.gov" target="_blank" rel="noopener">itd.idaho.gov</a></td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="last-updated"><em>Last updated: January 2026. Information based on Idaho Code 49-948. Always verify current conditions with Idaho 511 before traveling.</em></p>
    </div>
